{
  "stem": "25773.6",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But apparently the Germans, in the last effort, just before they knew they will collapse, they-- they made this terrific effort.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they won.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was not difficult to-- to win over the Polish revolutionaries, who were not [? too-- ?] well supplied with the-- with the arms like the-- like the Warsaw ghetto was not supplied with arms.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They were not-- they were-- the command was-- I think it was as certain-- maybe specially purposely, the information was not-- not quite right.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And-- and especially, the-- the devious Russian attitude of stopping at Praga, when they could in a few minutes be in a war zone finish the whole.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Deviously stopped in Praga and let the Polish revolutionaries bled-- bleed to death.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We were in the shelters.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We were tearing the-- the-- the-- sheets for bandages.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "There was not enough food.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "There was nothing at the hospital, there were not-- not enough nurses.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "There was not enough-- disorganized.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And all because the Polish people thought--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--once they started the revolution, the Russians would come in together, they liberate-- the Poles liberate Warsaw in their own right, in their own-- and then together they will defeat the Germans.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But it proved to be different.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The Germans were still quite strong.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They didn't-- were not strong, but they put a resistance.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They-- the revolution kept-- I mean, nearly eight weeks, completely defeated.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "A lot of people lost lives.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we were in the shelters.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we were very lucky, because one day young German soldiers arrived-- soldier arrived.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He said, [SPEAKING GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And [INAUDIBLE] were in the-- the children were-- they were starving, so we used to go out of the shelter.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We young, I and other-- my friend [?",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
